posts.title: NFT?
posts.preview_text: I am a prolific artist, and I live a life devoted to creativity. Am I successful? It depends on what you think is being successful. I have focused on developing ideas for my art and concepts for the last five years rather than my professional career. I don’t need to tell you that time seems to move faster as you age.
